ity should be seen - as a general pattern of sense, as good order or as individual care.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aApologeticsxHistoryyEarly church, ca. 30-600. 0aGodxAttributes. 0aProvidence and government of GodxHistory of doctrines. 4aApologetik. 4aFrühchristentum. 4aGriechisch. 4aSubstantiv. 4apronoia ‹Wort›. 7aRELIGION / Christian Theology / Ecclesiology.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Theology and Religious Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110638165oZDB-23-GTR0 cprintz978311017062740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311090571740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110905717423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110905717/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GTRc2000d2014